						<summary>

						<p>Dambe pillar in the Mahālingēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">1576 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>In this worn out record excepting the date all other information are lost.</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka 1498, Dhatri, Chaitra, śu. 10, Sunday corresponding to 1576 A.D., March, 10. The weekday was however, Saturday.</p>						

